DB Schema

USER
id (PK)
name
email (unique)
role (ADMIN / TEACHER / STUDENT)
is_status (boolean)
SUBJECT
id (PK)
subject_name
semester

STUDENT
id (PK)
user_id (FK → USER.id)
roll_no


TEACHER
id (PK)
user_id (FK → USER.id)


TEACHER_SUBJECT
id (PK)
teacher_id (FK → TEACHER.id)
subject_id (FK → SUBJECT.id)


MARKS
id (PK)
student_id (FK → STUDENT.id)
subject_id (FK → SUBJECT.id)
exam_type (IA1 / IA2 / IA3/Special)
marks
created_by_teacher_id (FK → TEACHER.id)
marks_proof_pdf LONGBLOB


OTP_EVENTS
id (PK)
user_id (FK → USER.id)
otp_code
purpose (REGISTRATION / LOGIN / PASSWORD_RESET)
expiry_time
status (PENDING / VERIFIED / EXPIRED)
created_at
